harmonic_sum(n):
  if n == 1:
    return 1
  else:
    return 1 / n + harmonic_sum(n - 1)
This will cause a SyntaxError because Python requires the `def` keyword to define a function. The student genuinely believes this is the correct way to define a function and doesn't suspect any issues.

